OL,3,CMet police announce survey into
OL,4,Ccontroversial stop and search
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police is asking
OL,7,FLondoners what they think about the
OL,8,Fcontroversial stop and search practice
OL,9,Fthrough a new survey.
OL,11,FIt's part of a new plan by the Met to
OL,12,Freset its relationship with London's
OL,13,Fcommunities and build back lost
OL,14,Fconfidence.
OL,16,FThe force believes that when done
OL,17,Fright, stop and search is an effective
OL,18,Ftool. It said officers take 4,000
OL,19,Fdangerous weapons off the streets
OL,20,Fevery year as a result of this tactic.
