OL,6,FBut when done poorly, it said, stop
OL,7,Fand search can have a detrimental
OL,8,Fimpact on the relationship between the
OL,9,Fpolice and local communities `
OL,10,Fespecially those who are
OL,11,Fdisproportionally affected by stop and
OL,12,Fsearch.
OL,14,FOver the past few months, teams across
OL,15,Fthe Met have been speaking to a range
OL,16,Fof people across the city including
OL,17,Fcharities, faith groups and youth
OL,18,Fgroups ` having open and frank
OL,19,Fdiscussions about stop and search.
