OL,4,Ccontroversial stop and search
OL,6,FThere are 32 questions in the online
OL,7,Fsurvey, which focus on the public
OL,8,Fperception of stop and search,
OL,9,Fpersonal experiences of the tactic,
OL,10,Ftraining for officers, and what could
OL,11,Fbe done better.
OL,13,FDeputy Assistant Commissioner Ade
OL,14,FAdelekan, who leads the project, said:
OL,15,F"A key part of our plan to reform the
OL,16,FMet is to work closely with our
OL,17,Fcommunities, ensuring we police with
OL,18,Ftheir consent.
