OL,4,Ccontroversial stop and search
OL,6,F"Stop and search has always been a
OL,7,Fcontentious issue. When used well it
OL,8,Fsaves lives and is important in
OL,9,Fkeeping Londoners safe, helping us
OL,10,Fidentify criminality and take
OL,11,Fdangerous weapons like knives and
OL,12,Ffirearms off our streets.
