OL,3,CMet police announce survey into
OL,4,Ccontroversial stop and search
OL,6,F"I know some Londoners have a poor
OL,7,Fexperience of stop and search and that
OL,8,Fhas damaged the trust, confidence and
OL,9,Fco-operation of some communities. That
OL,10,Fdistrust is higher in communities
OL,11,Fwhere stop and search powers are used
OL,12,Fmost often, generally where violent
OL,13,Fcrime, driven by a small minority, is
OL,14,Fhighest.
OL,16,F"This is why we are taking the first
OL,17,Fsteps to reset our approach. We want
OL,18,Fto hear from Londoners and create an
OL,19,Fagreement between the Met and the
OL,20,Fpublic on how we conduct stop and
OL,21,Fsearches in the future."
